(sv)
Soundtracket till ett datorspel som aldrig blev f&ouml;rverkligat.
Vissa element d&ouml;k dock upp i andra projekt.
Gitarr-riffet i "Dream Wheel" &auml;r samma som det i slutet av
"Betty's Body" fr&aring;n "Demons Dance Alone"-skivan.

(eng)
The soundtrack to a computer game that never was realized.
Some elements however, ended up in other projects.
The guitar riff in "Dream Wheel" is the same as the one at
the end of "Betty's Body" from the "Demons Dance Alone" album.
